@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "PO" as PO
participant ":System" as System
participant ":Parent Simulation Process" as ParentProcess
participant ":Safety Detection Thread" as SafetyThread
participant ":Report Generation Thread" as ReportThread

activate PO

PO -> System : Requests function-specific parent process threads

activate System
System -> ParentProcess : Initialize parent process threading model

activate ParentProcess
ParentProcess --> ParentProcess : Initialize mutexes
ParentProcess --> ParentProcess : Initialize condition variables

ParentProcess -> SafetyThread : Create safety violation detection thread

activate SafetyThread
SafetyThread --> SafetyThread : Prepare to scan shared memory
SafetyThread --> ParentProcess : Safety thread initialized
deactivate SafetyThread

ParentProcess -> ReportThread : Create report generation thread

activate ReportThread
ReportThread --> ReportThread : Prepare to compile simulation results
ReportThread --> ParentProcess : Report thread initialized
deactivate ReportThread

ParentProcess --> ParentProcess : Register thread responsibilities

alt all required threads created
    ParentProcess --> System : Threading model initialized
    System --> PO : Dedicated parent process threads created successfully
else thread creation fails
    ParentProcess --> ParentProcess : Clean up created threads and synchronization primitives
    ParentProcess --> System : Threading model initialization failed
    System --> PO : Display thread initialization error
end

deactivate ParentProcess
deactivate System
deactivate PO

@enduml